com.aylanetworks.aylasdk

类 AylaRulesService

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.aylanetworks.aylasdk.AylaRulesService

  • public class AylaRulesService
extends java.lang.Object
    AylaRulesService class is responsible for Creating,Fetching,Updating and Deleting Rules and Rule Actions. This class interacts with Rules Service in the Cloud that is a system of cloud components on the Ayla Platform that implement a rules framework and enable devices to interact with the outside world

      • fetchRules

        public AylaAPIRequest fetchRules(AylaRule.RuleType type,
                                 java.lang.String id,
                                 com.android.volley.Response.Listener<AylaRule[]> successListener,
                                 ErrorListener errorListener)
        Fetches an array of AylaRules from the cloud for the given type and id
        参数:
        type - null for Normal User. Mandatory for OEM/Ayla admin user. Valid values for OEM/Ayla admin user are device and user
        id - null for Normal User. Mandatory for OEM/Ayla admin user. Valid values for OEM/Ayla admin user are Device dsn and User uuid
        successListener - Listener to receive on successful fetch of AylaRules
        errorListener - Listener to receive an AylaError should one occur
        返回:
        the AylaAPIRequest object used to fetch Rules
